snippet.title: Desperate fight to save injured motorcycle rider
snippet.content:
PARAMEDICS are on scene performing CPR on a motorcycle rider after a single-vehicle crash.
The crash was reported just before midday on Hunchy Rd, Palmwoods.
The rider was described as being a man in his 40s.
